    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wooden instruments resembling a sword, paddle, or butcher's knife, used for beating and scraping flax, hemp, cotton, or other fibrous plant material in order to separate the fibers from woody or coarse particles.The tools may be hand-held or attached to a wheel.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
